/'
Diagram 2 — Keras Module Decomposition
(Subsystem Specialization & Responsibility View)

Diagram Purpose & Meaning:
This diagram refines the high-level Module View by exposing internal specialization
within subsystems. It reveals how architectural responsibilities are distributed.

Architectural clusters:
- Training monitoring: metrics
- Computation policy: initializers, regularizers, constraints, activations
- Deployment lifecycle: saving, export
- Performance scaling: distribution, mixed_precision
- Execution abstraction: ops, backend
'/

